http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.value: This is a list of international visits undertaken by Hillary Clinton (in office 2009–2013) while serving as the United States Secretary of State. The list includes both private travel and official state visits. The list includes only foreign travel which the Secretary of State made during her tenure in the position.
